  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You perform a 3-point strike in multiple points made to penetrate the target's defense. Make three melee taijutsu attacks with your weapon, dealing your weapons damage, do not add your ability modifier to damage dealt. The target must also make a constitution saving throw. On a failed save they gain one rank of weakened until the end of their next turn.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the target suffers a -1 penalty on their save. </p>",
